snippet.title: Amber Heard LIED About Giving Millions to Charity?!
snippet.description:
Amber Heard is being accused of skipping out on donating $7 million to charity, including $3.5 million to a Children's Hospital. Heard claimed under oath she had donated all of her Johnny Depp divorce settlement money to charity, but this doesn't seem to be true. So what ELSE did she lie about...?
